772
00:57:13,332 --> 00:57:14,572
Dan

773
00:57:16,651 --> 00:57:17,972
membunuh

774
00:57:18,972 --> 00:57:20,171
Putri Pyeonggang.

775
00:57:36,651 --> 00:57:39,451
Senang bisa berkumpul bersama.

776
00:57:39,691 --> 00:57:41,611
Tuan Putri datang.

777
00:57:43,371 --> 00:57:44,931
Hai, kamu di sini.

778
00:57:46,411 --> 00:57:48,572
Kukira ini panggilan penting.

779
00:57:48,572 --> 00:57:50,972
Kami ingin kamu menghirup
udara segar

780
00:57:50,972 --> 00:57:52,332
di luar Balai Magnolia.

781
00:57:52,332 --> 00:57:54,611
Ratu menyarankan agar kita
berkumpul untuk minum teh.

782
00:57:55,611 --> 00:57:57,812
Kita berkumpul setelah sekian lama.

783
00:57:57,812 --> 00:58:00,211
Jangan terlalu memikirkannya
dan duduklah.

