01:00:17,252 --> 01:00:18,611
Nona Hae kembali.

801
01:00:18,611 --> 01:00:21,851
Apa? Dia kembali?

802
01:00:26,492 --> 01:00:27,611
Nona Hae!

803
01:00:28,532 --> 01:00:29,772
Mo Yong!

804
01:00:32,691 --> 01:00:35,931
