01:01:52,131 --> 01:01:54,931
Apa maksudmu? Jaga ucapanmu.

821
01:01:54,931 --> 01:01:56,812
Tuan Putri pasti salah paham.

822
01:01:56,812 --> 01:01:58,292
Berhenti di sana, Go Won Pyo.

